"local" synctargettext="false" type="ncc-clause">D3D23</xref> or <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/5e2c1f63-e589-4ce1-95e8-5c3e286a7aff/3350_2.1.0.xml#_062ca954-1b3b-43db-82c0-8f4fd12a8f3f" id="_36e10c56-e885-478d-b688-223e821e1ded" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="ncc-clause">I3D5</xref>, and doorways, must be not less than—</p><ol outputclass="alpha"><li id="_d7f8045e-6527-4580-a966-e343e3b35a5b">1 m; or</li><li id="_ec07e219-40f0-4bec-a522-879499647a62">1.8 m in a passageway, corridor or ramp normally used for the transportation of patients in beds within a <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/5e2c1f63-e589-4ce1-95e8-5c3e286a7aff/1499_27.0.0.xml#_0a15b45c-4a85-4ba1-aea2-b0b36035d808" id="_2030ef5f-2f72-4d9f-b1c0-092b89b079c6" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">treatment area</xref> or <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/5e2c1f63-e589-4ce1-95e8-5c3e286a7aff/1512_27.0.0.xml#_d1b612a5-df98-4406-ba1e-237f837e1061" id="_d4710576-7539-4395-8f8a-87797a25bb66" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">ward area</xref>; and</li><li id="_8e3fcd72-f8e2-403f-8f93-2c5c765fa25d">in a <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/5e2c1f63-e589-4ce1-95e8-5c3e286a7aff/1419_4.0.0.xml#_eea79623-bc7d-4ef1-b787-8452b6383ffc" id="_b9a5fc06-5ea1-47c4-8b86-41fd476dbbb2" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">public corridor</xref> in a Class 9c <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/5e2c1f63-e589-4ce1-95e8-5c3e286a7aff/1180_1.0.0.xml#_41ac03c9-62e4-45df-84a3-8f31abb6b147" id="_21dce488-c1db-41bc-9f5f-741ddb558b14" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">aged care building</xref>, notwithstanding (2) and (3)—<ol><li>1.5 m; and</li><li>1.8 m for the full width of the doorway, providing access into a <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/5e2c1f63-e589-4ce1-95e8-5c3e286a7aff/1473_0.4.0.xml#_d2c89488-8a36-464b-94f6-a91d0f5a6c9c" id="_5311f5a7-1af8-434b-ae68-7de082285bad" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">sole-occupancy unit</xref> or communal bathroom.</li></ol></li></ol></subclause><subclause id="_b267d0a0-2c65-448a-99bc-c6d1a0eb4b57" outputclass="subclause"><title id="_4bd632c2-0e92-4db0-a37b-5ca6ccc996ff">SubClause</title><num>2</num><p>If <xt:delText xt:action="start" xt:author="Jerome Samuel" xt:dateTime="2024-03-08T08:59:00" xt:id="7a236ab7-7fde-44ff-a5b4-6ef0d29fc947"/>the<xt:delText xt:action="end" xt:id="7a236ab7-7fde-44ff-a5b4-6ef0d29fc947"/><xt:insText xt:action="start" xt:author="Jerome Samuel" xt:dateTime="2024-03-08T08:59:00" xt:id="28ac4ec4-0514-4e65-851e-d312b8f9c942"/>a <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/5e2c1f63-e589-4ce1-95e8-5c3e286a7aff/1277_2.0.0.xml#_524b0326-5823-4ddc-9eb3-adab587568e8" id="_b0ed598e-c3f0-434d-b323-e5b4e789fa1d" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">fire compartment</xref> relying on one or more <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/5e2c1f63-e589-4ce1-95e8-5c3e286a7aff/1340_2.0.0.xml#_45cfdc7e-cb0d-4318-95cc-462e079e9b9c" id="_85c225fd-d4e4-4b82-b106-e07a2ad67ebb" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">horizontal exits</xref>, a<xt:insText xt:action="end" xt:id="28ac4ec4-0514-4e65-851e-d312b8f9c942"/> <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/5e2c1f63-e589-4ce1-95e8-5c3e286a7aff/1483_25.0.0.xml#_53ff3ea1-55e7-4f2a-b2b3-ca445ff64c15" id="_0e785ded-b6c8-4adb-a9a0-16579afad5c2" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">storey</xref>,<xt:insText xt:action="start" xt:author="Jerome Samuel" xt:dateTime="2024-08-28T12:46:00" xt:id="fa2afbca-8a3c-46b2-86c8-f755000cd9c5"/> a<xt:insText xt:action="end" xt:id="fa2afbca-8a3c-46b2-86c8-f755000cd9c5"/> <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/5e2c1f63-e589-4ce1-95e8-5c3e286a7aff/1373_0.6.0.xml#_f68246d9-7a77-41fc-8050-516881323e47" id="_715c324e-7e33-4898-8209-0f0ce5450ab1" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">mezzanine</xref> or <xt:insTex